/index.html      ← homepage + brief intro, navigation  
/about.html      ← who you are, what the site is for  
/market.html     ← trade journal / notes / saved charts  
/tools.html      ← JS-based tools you build (or embed widgets)  
/assets/         ← CSS, JS, images folder  
/style.css       ← basic styling  
/script.js       ← logic / chart fetching / overlays  
